Years of Refusal is the forthcoming ninth solo album by Morrissey. Distributed by Decca in the UK and Lost Highway in the US, it is set for release on 16 February 2009 and 17 February 2009 respectively. Morrissey has described his newest album as his strongest.


The Band:

    Morrissey - Vocals
    Boz Boorer - Guitars, Clarinet, Drums
    Jesse Tobias - Guitars
    Solomon Walker - Bass guitar
    Matt Walker - Drums
    Roger Manning - Keyboards
    Jeff Beck - Guitar (Black Cloud)
    Michael Farrell - Keyboards (That's How People Grow Up)
    Kristeen Young - Backing vocals (That's How People Grow Up)
